data.description: Income-producing property, live on one side and rent out the other to help make the payment.  (2946/2948 Robert Road)   All brick with little painting on the exterior.   Each unit has 2 bedrooms and 2 baths, with central heat and air. Each unit has a washer & dryer hookup. Covered back porches.  Fully fenced with privacy fencing, and each side has its own utility storage building.  Easy access to Hwy 177 and I-40.
